sellerCard.description:
Hello, Welcome on my profile.

Are you looking for a creative WordPress website designer & developer? 

I am a software engineer with a passion to develop websites to help people bring their businesses to the internet. I mainly create and customize business directory websites.

Hit me up to know more about my expertise or if you have any questions.

description.content:
Develop, Design, redesign and much more


I will deliver a complete and ready-to-publish WordPress directory website with a custom design built with wp geodirectory and elementor pro


Features:

  • Custom Designed Preview Card, Detail/Single Page and Search Page
  • Event Listing with Ticket Selling
  • Sell Text, Banner, HTML and Listings Ads by a number of impressions, clicks, or by time
  • Advertising Dashboard
  • Free, Paid listing Subscriptions with Trial Period
  • Admin or Auto Approval
  • Basic & Advanced Search Filteration
  • Verify Listings
  • Reviews & Comments
  • Fully Secured Payment Gateway (Paypal, Stripe, Woocommerce Payments)
  • Google map/Open street map integration
  • Login/Register System
  • Social Logins
  • Recaptcha to avoid spam

**Translation of the website will require a separate quote.


This gig does not include data scraping or data mining. If you want to bulk import listings on the website. Please check my data scraping gig (link below) for prices and delivery time.

https://www.fiverr.com/s2/1fa19067e8

ï»¿

***Prices may vary based on design customizations. Ping me to see my work samples so you can see my work speaks for my price. If you are low on budget but want top-quality work just ping m
